The Christmas songs chosen so far are "I saw three ships", "O come, o come, Emmanuel" and "The first Noël", with the hat decoration by Janette Tozer, a local artist.
Martin Poole, 50, a TV marketing assistant from Hove, is a volunteer minister in the Diocese of Chichester and head of Beyond.
