Why do we as a church expect people to come into a strange old building? I think the church should go to the people and have exciting celebrations.
The idea for the Beach Lodge Advent Calendar started as a conversation with some friends over dinner.
Brighton is such a fantastically creative and vibrant place and we try to express that through our spirituality".
