Johnny Hallyday has had another operation, RTL confirms he's been put into an artificial coma
Johnny Hallyday was operated on again in Los Angeles for significant "damage" after an operation in France, and according to those around him, the situation was "under control", although RTL confirmed that the singer was put into an artificial coma to avoid pain and complications.
